---
title: Creamy Honey Mustard Chicken with Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: Dinner tonight proves, once and for all, why honey and mustard is a winning combo. Just add cream and a little chicken stock, and you get a sauce that's so sublime you'll be scraping up every last bit.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-honey-mustard-chicken-455d46a7.jpg
